# Parking Lots API

### Get all parking lots 
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ParkingLots
Content-Type: application/json

### Get a specific parking lot by ID 
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ParkingLots/{{parkingLotId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Create a new parking lot
# @name newParkingLot
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ParkingLots
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Shopping Center Garage",
  "address": "789 Mall Ave, Suburbia",
  "description": "Covered parking with direct mall access.",
  "operatingHours": "Mon-Sun 8am-12am",
  "latitude": 34.0567,
  "longitude": -118.2499
}

### Update an existing parking lot
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/ParkingLots/{{parkingLotId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Downtown Parking (Updated)",
  "address": "123 Main St, Downtown (Renovated)",
  "description": "Central parking facility with multiple levels. Now with EV charging.",
  "operatingHours": "24/7",
  "latitude": 40.7129,
  "longitude": -74.0061
}

### Delete a parking lot
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/ParkingLots/{{parkingLotId}}
Content-Type: application/json


# Reservations API

### Get all reservations
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Reservations
Content-Type: application/json

### Get reservation by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Reservations/{{reservationId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get reservations by user ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Reservations/user/{{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get reservations by parking spot ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Reservations/spot/{{parkingSpotId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Create a new reservation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startTime": "2025-12-01T10:00:00",
  "endTime": "2025-12-01T12:00:00",
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "carId": "{{carId}}",
  "parkingSpotId": "{{parkingSpotId}}"
}

### Update reservation status (Example: Set to 'Completed')
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/Reservations/{{reservationId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": 2
}

### Cancel a reservation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Reservations/{{reservationId}}/cancel
Content-Type: application/json



